Name: An Afrikaans spellchecking dictionary
URL: http://zaf.svn.sourceforge.net/viewvc/zaf/trunk/dict/
Version: 1.0
Update Mechanism: Manual (https://crbug.com/422924034)
License File: README-af-ZA.txt
Security Critical: no
Shipped: yes
Description:
This folder contains a partial copy of the Afrikaans dictionary for hunspell. It consists of a dictionary file, an affix file, and a license file. (It does not include installation scripts used by Firefox.)
